{"tid":2043196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約公車司機工會拒為警察押送被捕示威者","createTime":"2020-05-30T09:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T09:55:44.000Z","uid":40267,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3dccb2f2bf1f4a18641b5ffe999489d134cabf35","tid":2043196,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:05:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/m7jed3/nyc-bus-drivers-union-refuses-to-tra\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vice.com%2Fen_us%2Farticle%2Fm7jed3%2Fnyc-bus-drivers-union-refuses-to-tra&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD%2BTimN4xbKJd0qqIWjmG9ok%3D&h=5f67fc7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/m7jed3/nyc-bus-drivers-union-refuses-to-tra</a><br />\n<br />\n紐約市MTA的工人正拒絕運送在明尼阿波利斯警方殺害George Floyd事件發生後在反警暴抗議期間被捕的人。 一名公車司機拒絕運送在布魯克林巴克萊中心（Barclays Center）門前的抗議活動中被捕的人的影片在週五晚上被瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n在影片中，一群人正為一名似乎拒絕坐在駕駛座的公車司機喝彩。 「紐約警方正在用公車運輸在巴克萊中心被捕的抗議者，」分享這段影片的@berniebromanny在推特上寫道。 「然而，公車司機拒絕駕駛它。」這段影片在短短一個多小時的時間裡，就有超過100萬次的<br />\n瀏覽量。<br />\n<br />\nMotherboard (Vice旗下的一個部門）已經去確認，這是代表MTA公車司機工會的官方立場<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n「我們的任何公車都不應該被用來做這種事。 我們在佔領華爾街事件期間因不載運上了<br />\n法院，」當被問及工會是否會運送被逮捕的人時，代表該市公車司機的Transit Workers Union Local 100的副主席JP Patafio這樣告訴Motherboard。<br />\n<br />\n「我告訴MTA，我們的公車不會被用來四處載運警察，」他補充說， 「這是在聲援明尼阿波利斯市的公車司機。」<br />\n<br />\n2011年，該工會提起訴訟，阻止紐約警察局徵用公車，強迫城市司機為警察運送被捕的「佔領華爾街」抗議者。<br />\n<br />\n最近幾天，明尼阿波利斯市的公車司機同樣拒絕為警察運送被捕的抗議者，全市各地的工會司機也紛紛表示聲援抗議者，他們更明確的抗議警察殺害George Floyd和警察的暴行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83e8b75883dcdcd5e6fc83e8721b1dbe333ccba","tid":2043196,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"78548eb78f4c16df16c003ca6b915a09ac53b794","tid":2043196,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7e6772bfd654da934d154445e2f20c64161cb7","tid":2043196,"uid":59913,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"我剩係知巴士，推車我識，但係唔識咩叫公車"},{"pid":"403c1bb86b12a22f212d65d7f457fabda4bd9212","tid":2043196,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"Go to school by<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">[ 港獨強心針 ]  用15分鐘來認清香港最強力盟友USA : 國際反共形勢大好，咪撚再灰！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2041520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2041520</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"3c608274776f6d374da9afbe6ea2f068b0318fab","tid":2043196,"uid":221055,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:19:12.000Z","msg":"如果喺香港，連個司機都拉埋"},{"pid":"6fec1d0c2452669d26c87211ce0ce6d596ee44c4","tid":2043196,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"美國一樣大把黑警"},{"pid":"282ba54c7979dd5603dfa0f1e3c791631f6b4083","tid":2043196,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fec1d0c2452669d26c87211ce0ce6d596ee44c4","tid":2043196,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"美國一樣大把黑警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:23:19.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre